
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-eckert-anima-noc-autoconfig-00.txt'>
    <title>"Autoconfiguration of NOC services in ACP networks via GRASP", Toerless Eckert</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-eckert-anima-noc-autoconfig-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document defines standards for the autoconfiguration of crucial NOC services on ACP nodes via GRASP.  It enables secure remote access to zero-touch bootstrapped ANI devices via SSH/Netconf with Radius/ Diameter authentication and authorization and provides lifecycle autoconfiguration for other crucial services such as syslog, NTP (clock synchronization) and DNS for operational purposes.</description>
    <dc:date>2018-07-02T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
